data.description:
This immaculate 5-bedroom, 2-bathroom home is perfectly situated near schools and a park, making it an ideal find. With it's large open floor plan, this house offers plenty of space for both relaxation and entertaining. The finished basement provides additional living area, while the ample storage space ensures that everything has its place.
What sets this property apart is the extra separate 576 sq.ft. rental unit with a full kitchen. This versatile space can be used as an in-law suite or rented out for additional income. Complete with 1 bedroom and 1 bathroom, it offers privacy and convenience.  The two homes are separated by a privacy fence.  
Outside, you'll find a fully fenced yard, perfect for pets or children to play safely. Plus, with the newly installed heat/cool pump, you'll stay comfortable all year round.
Don't miss out on this incredible opportunity to own a spacious home with endless possibilities. Schedule your viewing today!
